<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<PcGts xmlns="http://schema.primaresearch.org/PAGE/gts/pagecontent/2019-07-15" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://schema.primaresearch.org/PAGE/gts/pagecontent/2019-07-15 http://schema.primaresearch.org/PAGE/gts/pagecontent/2019-07-15/pagecontent.xsd"><Metadata><Creator>xl-export</Creator><Created>2026-03-19T00:00:00Z</Created><LastChange>2026-03-19T00:00:00Z</LastChange></Metadata><Page imageFilename="" imageWidth="1000" imageHeight="1000"><TextRegion id="r1" custom="type:paragraph"><Coords points="0,0 1000,0 1000,1000 0,1000" /><TextLine id="l1" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,0 1000,0 1000,31 0,31" /><Baseline points="0,29 1000,29" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>Erfurt in the winter of 1435, and then, with more</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l2" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,31 1000,31 1000,62 0,62" /><Baseline points="0,60 1000,60" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>difficulty, traced that copy to me.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l3" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,62 1000,62 1000,93 0,93" /><Baseline points="0,91 1000,91" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>He was not writing to accuse me.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l4" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,93 1000,93 1000,124 0,124" /><Baseline points="0,122 1000,122" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>He was writing because Richter's press had recently</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l5" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,124 1000,124 1000,155 0,155" /><Baseline points="0,153 1000,153" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>completed an edition of selected Eckhart sermons, and the</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l6" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,155 1000,155 1000,186 0,186" /><Baseline points="0,184 1000,184" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>compositor — working from a manuscript in the Strasbourg</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l7" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,186 1000,186 1000,217 0,217" /><Baseline points="0,215 1000,215" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>house's collection, which descended from mine — had set the</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l8" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,217 1000,217 1000,248 0,248" /><Baseline points="0,246 1000,246" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>twelfth sermon with the variant reading.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l9" custom="register:verbatim_mhg"><Coords points="0,248 1000,248 1000,279 0,279" /><Baseline points="0,277 1000,277" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>Wirt.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l10" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,279 1000,279 1000,310 0,310" /><Baseline points="0,308 1000,308" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>Becomes.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l11" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,310 1000,310 1000,341 0,341" /><Baseline points="0,339 1000,339" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>He enclosed a single printed leaf. The relevant page. He</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l12" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,341 1000,341 1000,372 0,372" /><Baseline points="0,370 1000,370" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>said he thought I should know, as the reading's apparent</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l13" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,372 1000,372 1000,403 0,403" /><Baseline points="0,401 1000,401" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>origin, that it had now been committed to type in an edition</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l14" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,403 1000,403 1000,434 0,434" /><Baseline points="0,432 1000,432" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>of three hundred copies already distributed to houses in</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l15" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,434 1000,434 1000,465 0,465" /><Baseline points="0,463 1000,463" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>four cities, and that he personally found the reading</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l16" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,465 1000,465 1000,496 0,496" /><Baseline points="0,494 1000,494" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>theologically superior to the alternatives and intended to</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l17" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,496 1000,496 1000,527 0,527" /><Baseline points="0,525 1000,525" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>argue for its acceptance in the study he was preparing, and</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l18" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,527 1000,527 1000,558 0,558" /><Baseline points="0,556 1000,556" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>that if I had any documentation of my reasoning in selecting</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l19" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,558 1000,558 1000,589 0,589" /><Baseline points="0,587 1000,587" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>it he would be grateful to receive it.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l20" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,589 1000,589 1000,620 0,620" /><Baseline points="0,618 1000,618" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>I held the leaf for a long time.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l21" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,620 1000,620 1000,651 0,651" /><Baseline points="0,649 1000,649" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>The type was clean. The impression even. The word sat in the</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l22" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,651 1000,651 1000,682 0,682" /><Baseline points="0,680 1000,680" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>middle of Eckhart's sentence exactly where I had put it</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l23" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,682 1000,682 1000,713 0,713" /><Baseline points="0,711 1000,711" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>twenty-two years ago, wearing Eckhart's voice, surrounded by</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l24" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,713 1000,713 1000,744 0,744" /><Baseline points="0,742 1000,742" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>Eckhart's words, indistinguishable from the rest — as I had</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l25" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,744 1000,744 1000,775 0,775" /><Baseline points="0,773 1000,773" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>intended, as I had feared, as I had carried like a stone in</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l26" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,775 1000,775 1000,806 0,806" /><Baseline points="0,804 1000,804" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>my chest through two decades of Psalters and Gospels and one</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l27" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,806 1000,806 1000,837 0,837" /><Baseline points="0,835 1000,835" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>secret manuscript that I had been intending to burn since</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l28" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,837 1000,837 1000,868 0,868" /><Baseline points="0,866 1000,866" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>September and had not burned.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l29" custom="register:verbatim_mhg"><Coords points="0,868 1000,868 1000,899 0,899" /><Baseline points="0,897 1000,897" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>Wirt.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l30" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,899 1000,899 1000,930 0,930" /><Baseline points="0,928 1000,928" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>It looked, in type, exactly as it had looked in my hand.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l31" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,930 1000,930 1000,961 0,961" /><Baseline points="0,959 1000,959" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>Which is to say: it looked like Eckhart. It looked like it</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l32" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,961 1000,961 1000,992 0,992" /><Baseline points="0,990 1000,990" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>had always been there. It looked like the truth, which is</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine></TextRegion></Page></PcGts>